Headquarters Regions: Greater Los Angeles Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Your legal concerns deserve vigorous and aggressive representation with attention to your needs. At the Desai Family Law Group, we are dedicated to using the best solution to solve your legal problem, whether that solution is a negotiated settlement, mediation or a trial. At the Desai Family Law Group we understand the challenges our clients face today, but we always are looking out for your future best interests. We work to obtain the best possible results for you and your family. Family law matters are often emotionally difficult. It can be a delicate balancing act to protect your interests today while also considering your needs and your child's needs in the future. How you choose to work through sensitive issues now can have a profound affect on relationships later on. A good family law attorney can greatly ease the confusion, frustration, even hostility that a person may be feeling when they are in the difficult process of a divorce. When families are disrupted because of custody disputes, child support disagreements, or parenting time issues, a trusted family lawyer can protect you, point you in the direction of needed services and effective dispute resolution techniques, and help you ensure that these difficulties do not unduly interrupt your own or your kids' lives. An effective trial attorney can help you enforce child support or spousal maintenance orders, help protect you and your children from domestic violence, restore denied visitation, or fight to modify orders when circumstances have substantially changed. Contact the Desai Family Law Group if you are seeking a family lawyer or divorce attorney who will truly listen and work with you in a cooperative partnership to address your concerns and meet your goals. Our office is conveniently located off the 55 and 91 freeways. Evening appointments are available. I'm sure you have many questions. For a Free Consultation, please call us at (714) 637-1712 and we will be more than glad to offer you our advice.

Headquarters Regions: East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: Founded in 2010, PsycView focuses on developing telemedicine applications for physicians and therapists.  These applications are used to bridge the gap between physicians in cities who are lacking patients, and patients who live in underserved areas who would otherwise go untreated. The initial research for the software began by surveying therapists directly to gauge opinions on therapy-via-distance.  The results of this Phase I data closely matched existing studies on distance therapy from Stanford, and the decision was made to go forward with the project. After a more in-depth review of the market, it became clear that physicians had a very precise set of needs that are not currently being met by other solutions.  Phase II requested input on specific features. Phase III research is focused on physicians' response to telemedicine in general, as well as practice-specific questions.  Once Phase III is completed in June 2010, PsycView will be seeking Angel funding.
